{"tid":2416371,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"陳茂波：下年度將有較大赤字選擇有限　冀守望相助","createTime":"2021-02-21T03:55:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T04:49:54.000Z","uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5c55b2616616d73ac043ba48ecc69aace5e7a86e","tid":2416371,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:55:40.000Z","msg":"財政司長陳茂波發表網誌，指星期三發表的財政預算案，已經準備就緒，政府應對經濟下行及推出防疫抗疫措施，令今個年度的財政赤字急升至歷史新高。在經濟尚未恢復之際，政府須維持逆周期政策，發揮穩定作用，下年度會出現較大的赤字，為新一份預算案定下甚具挑戰的前設，難免令選擇有限，但他希望大家仍能守望相助，積極樂觀面對，指變幻不定的環境將使大家變得更敏銳、更有韌力。 <br />\n<br />\n網誌的相片顯示新一份預算案封面是青綠色，陳茂波表示，是代表著對未來所懷抱的希望，形容經濟和財政狀況有如植物生長，有周期和規律，不管是小草或大樹，起點都是小小的種子，但潛藏無限生機。"},{"pid":"01b89a6c31f82605734b8aa55167f9adbd791691","tid":2416371,"uid":50502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:58:46.000Z","msg":"波叔：<a href=\"http://大家上budget.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%8Abudget.gov.hk&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=f1599d4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">大家上budget.gov.hk</a> 講比我聽下你地意見啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n: 咩話？原來你地想加稅 好啦咁我回應你地既訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b04fb9fcf1385aff8a0ebbed04b44773a1699d","tid":2416371,"uid":113085,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T04:00:11.000Z","msg":"加印花稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab8b9ce3817fc8d66fbc8ec9968dc7416cf2134c","tid":2416371,"uid":287422,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T04:00:39.000Z","msg":"減你人工先啦！柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f